            secundo, die vero sexta mensis novembris, hora nonarum vel quasi, indiccione
            quintadecima, pontificatus sanctissimi in Christo patris et domini nostri Bonifacii,
            digna dei providencia pape nono, anno tercio. <rs type="fn" role="witness">In Gegenwart
              des <rs type="person" ref="pe__leonhard_schaur_QGW_II_I_1242">Leonardus Schaur, <roleName type="title">licenciatus in Decretis</roleName>, Ratisponensis et Pataviensis
                  <roleName type="title">ecclesiarum canonicus</roleName> et <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__passau-domkapitel">officialis curie</roleName> Pataviensis</rs>, des
                <rs type="person" ref="pe__simon_QGW_II_I_1242"><roleName type="prof">Notars</roleName> Simon, <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__ulrich_von_efferding_QGW_II_I_1242"><add>Sohn</add></roleName> quondam <rs type="person" ref="pe__ulrich_von_efferding_QGW_II_I_1242">Ulrici de Everding</rs>, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__passau-dioezese">clericus</roleName> Pataviensis diocesis</rs>, und
              der <rs type="person" ref="pe__leopold_ulrici_de_wienna_QGW_II_I_1242">Zeugen Leopoldus, Ulrici de
                Wienna, <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_stephan-altar_zwoelfapostel">Rectors</roleName> des Apostelaltars in der Stephanskirche</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__thomas_de_attenshaim_QGW_II_I_1242"><add>Zeuge</add> Thoma de Attenshaim,
                  <roleName type="prof">Priesters</roleName> der Passauer Diöcese</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="pe__niklas_theoderici_de_jaur_QGW_II_I_1242">Nicolaus, Theoderici de Jaur,
                  <roleName type="prof">Priesters</roleName> der Breslauer Diöcese</rs></rs>,
              <triggerstring n="disp">legt <add>Urkunde vor</add></triggerstring>
            <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="pe__johann_von_eslarn_QGW_II_I_1242">Johannes,
                  <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__wien-st_maria_im_rathaus">rector</roleName>
                capelle beate Marie virginis in Ottenhaim Wienne</rs></rs>, eine von <rs type="fn" role="recipient">
              <rs type="person" ref="pe__siegfried_reicholf_QGW_II_I_1242">Seifrid, weiln gesessen an des herzogen
                  <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__albrecht_herzog_von_oesterreich_QGW_II_I_1020">stat</roleName>
                <roleName type="occ" corresp="org__oesterreich-herzogtum" select="pl__wien">anwalt
                  in der münz ze Wienn</roleName></rs>, und seiner <rs type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_405"><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__siegfried_reicholf_QGW_II_I_1242">Hausfrau</roleName> Margret</rs></rs> am 10.
            April 1356 ausgestellte Urkunde vor (vgl. Urk. no 478 a), welche von dem genannten Notar
              <triggerstring n="disp">vidimiert wird</triggerstring>.</rs></p></div><div type="nota"><p/></div><div type="lists"><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/placeList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/personList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/eventList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/><xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../indices/orgList.xml" xpointer="element(/1/2/1/1)"/></div></body></text></TEI>